# Team Names File Format
# Format: TeamID, Team Name, Institution, Member1, Member2, ...
# 
# TeamID should match the team's ID (0-indexed or as needed)
# Institution is optional but recommended
# Members are optional
#
# Example entries:

0, Harvard A, Harvard University, Alice Johnson, Bob Smith
1, Yale A, Yale University, Carol Davis, David Lee
2, Stanford A, Stanford University, Emma Wilson, Frank Chen
3, MIT A, Massachusetts Institute of Technology, Grace Taylor, Henry Martinez
4, Princeton A, Princeton University, Iris Anderson, Jack Robinson
5, Columbia A, Columbia University, Kelly White, Leo Harris

